Minsk weather summary for coming week

The maximum temperature for Minsk over the next 7 day will be 36C(or 97C) on Tuesday 11th August at around 2 pm. In the same week the minimum temperature will be 18C (or 64C) on Friday 7th August at around 5 am. Our Minsk weather forecaster is reporting Monday 10th August to be the wettest day in the coming week with around 2.30mm (or 0.1 inches) of rainfall. Make sure to carry an umbrella if you are out and about in Minsk. The windiest of all days will be Thursday 13th August as wind will reach 10mph (or 15kmph) at around 5 pm.
